Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Chopper! It's not a holoholo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it used to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only technology of the future\Ncould make it work...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too old?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was an advanced kingdom\Nlike Egghead 900 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Forbidden Piece of History!\NA Theory Concerning a Kingdom"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,900 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean a futuristic city like this\Nexisted that many years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who once risked his life\Nfor archaeology...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shed light on a certain ancient kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the manufacture of machinery\Nwhich has been discovered at a certain site...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...coincides with\Nthe reign of that kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that machine built\Nduring the 100-Year Void?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Do you know something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you don't even want to think back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but 22 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your birthplace Ohara was destroyed\Nby the Navy's Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's because Ohara learned of\Nthe existence of that kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 100-Year Void...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...contains the history of the conflict\Nbetween the advanced kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Twenty Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Twenty Kingdoms who won the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...later founded the World Government\Nand created the world as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to prevent anyone from\Ninheriting that ancient kingdom's ideology,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they erased it completely from history.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an exciting story!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too grand a story\Nfor me to comprehend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I mean, "erase completely"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ohara received a Buster Call\Nbecause of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that means people who learn about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We didn't even ask!\NWhy did you tell us about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I've heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget it! I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear a thing!\NI don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I didn't hear a thing! Forget it!\N--Calm down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I didn't hear anything! Forget it!\N--I said it was just a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ohara was destroyed\Nbecause of this theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think that means the Government\Nhas admitted it to be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vegapunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scholars of Ohara continued to study\Nthe valuable materials and made a theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a position as high as yours,\Nwould the Government tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they didn't tell me anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rule still stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm affiliated with the Government,\NI'll be killed if I mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how did you find out\Nabout the kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The books that Ohara acquired\Nfrom all over the world must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The will of Ohara lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day,\Nthe world was thrown into confusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara, an academic island with\Nthe most advanced knowledge in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was destroyed overnight\Nleaving just one girl behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara was accused of being an evil group of scholars\Nplotting to overthrow the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several months after the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I visited Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I knew the late Professor Clover,\Nthe archaeologic czar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to lay flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was obsessed with the 100-Year Void,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and went on adventures\Nto scour the world for documents about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:07:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was arrested by the Navy,\Nand jailed ten times...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he became\Nthe most famous archaeologist in the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eventually,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}scholars who were impressed by him\Ncame together at Ohara,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the island became\Nthe center for archaeology.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say the tragedy occurred\Nbecause he was talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past belongs to all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has the right to stop one from\Nwanting to know our unspoken history!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By analyzing the ancient\Ndocuments and some Ponegliffs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we eventually noticed\Nthe existence of a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no trace of it left now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what the documents brought to light\Nwas the existence of a grand kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it seems to have\Nboasted much power in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the information on this country\Nhas obsessively been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably sensed they'd be\Ndefeated by the allied countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,later to become the World Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so inscribed all the truth on\Nstones to pass it down to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, those stones are the Ponegliffs\Nthat remain to this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's a bold hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the Ancient Weapon\Nwould threaten the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, isn't it actually that the\NWorld Government is more threatened
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by people becoming aware of that\Nkingdom's existence and ideology?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this once-prosperous\Nkingdom that holds the key to everything is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara has...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come to know too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the attack signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll initiate a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I set foot on Ohara,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the place was an absolute disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the Tree of Knowledge\Nwas burned to the ground,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it seemed like everything\Nwas reduced to ashes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I walked deeper into the island,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I witnessed something astonishing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A vast amount of books of all kinds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...were submerged in the lake\Nat the center of the island!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps the scholars stayed on the island\Nwhich was burning under the Buster Call,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and died protecting the legacy\Nthey were to leave for the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The books that so many scholars protected\Nat the risk of their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if ignorant soldiers found them,\Nthey wouldn't know how valuable they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a victory for Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop my tears from falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let my daughter escape\Nfrom the island at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No! What about you, Mom?!\NAren't you gonna come with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olvia... What are you gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something\Nthat I have to do here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! I don't wanna be separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an Ohara scholar,\Nso you should know this very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,History is the treasure of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll certainly light up the future\Nyou young ones will live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the history we received\Nfrom the past will disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless we pass it on to the next era.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Put out the fire!\N--Protect the books!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save as many books as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw the books out of the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revealing the history isn't\Nwhat Ohara was trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted to accept the voices\Nof the past and protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our research will end now,\Nbut even if Ohara is obliterated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we cannot give up the future\Nyou young ones will live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will understand someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll stay here, too! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom is honorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday,\Npass down this island's history, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara fought against the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How dare you make her cry,\Nyou helmet fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Unforgivable! Vegapunk! I'll kick you!\N--Gee! How insensitive you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So get these shoes off me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get them off!\N--Look at me, you damn helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you guessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara uncovered\Nthe existence of the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the books...\Nthat were in the lake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to bring them back\Nto Punk Hazard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if the higher-ups heard about it,\Nit would all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into those guys that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's no cockpit on this thing, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't checked under its jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Franky has its cockpit\Nat the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since this is so big,\Nit could be someplace we never imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Chopper.\NWhen there is a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we've got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates Docking Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a robot warrior on a search mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our combined power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:54.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SCRAP HEAP, FABRIOPHASE\NEGGHEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Rocket Booster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where is the cockpit?!\N--I guess you can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dream come true for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any door? I don't think it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's on its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's get down then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, behind me there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sorry!\N--Don't move your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear what I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did they combine for after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there is no no cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Maybe this robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is autonomous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one of those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'll react\Nif we say something to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like... Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Move, robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the magic phrase is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It must have a name!\NWe should call that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Robonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it by different names!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Robomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Big Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Robotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Miracle Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robo Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robo King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee... What are you guys, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way\Nyou could get it to work like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?! The robot exploded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me-{\i1}Quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quasar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I failed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, help me-{\i1}Quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe space-time distorted\Nwhile I was warping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that old man there before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sinking! Hey!\N--I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on.\NOld man, do you need help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me-{\i1}Quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... You're just like Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dragon's son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were here. I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you doing well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, are you floating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Dom Shoes have a hover function!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A hover function?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we use it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, press the button on the side...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this lever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Push it further down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've flown too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me-{\i1}Quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:20:00.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,MAN WITH THE BEST BRAIN IN THE WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man with the best brain in the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A genius scientist, Dr. Vegapunk, appears!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,LEADER OF THE NAVY'S SPECIAL SCIENCE GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The real promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Tell Me, Robin!\NChopper's I-Wanna-Learn-More-You-Fool!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! I'm Chopper,\Nthe ship's doctor of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Robin, an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, I can't wait to learn as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information can be a strong weapon.\NLet's keep learning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Today we'll learn about this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaguar D. Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a Giant\Nand a former Navy Vice Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and Kuzan, also a former Navy officer,\Nwere close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born on March 6th\Nand likes roasted whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he met my mother Olvia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he began to question\Nthe Navy's brand of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he ran away from the Navy\Nalong with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He washed ashore on Ohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he protected me from the Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone now, but you'll\Nmeet friends someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends\Nwho'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:23:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took over this segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A scientist with an inner passion{\i0}
